<L>__{exterior columbine street day}
<A>__{nick and linda are some distance away. nick is shaking hands with an enthusiastic man while linda stands to one side, watching his face, and so full of love that she seems about to burst. another man comes over. linda takes the man's arm and presents him to nick.}
<B>__{we cannot hear what is being said. the only sound comes from the mill which looms up behind them out the frozen valley below.}
